<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Foreign Affairs:</header><text>Mr. Bilirakis.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Natural Resources:</header><text>Ms. Fallin and Mr. McCarthy of California.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

